### ðŸ”‘ **License Types Summary**

| **License Type**                   | **Used For**                                                                |
| ---------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Power Apps Premium**             | Advanced apps using Dataverse, premium connectors                           |
| **Power Automate Premium**         | Cloud flows with premium connectors, Dataverse, HTTP, etc.                  |
| **Power Automate Process License** | Run unattended desktop flows triggered via cloud flows (shared team use)    |
| **PAD RPA (Attended/Unattended)**  | Desktop automation, either with user presence (attended) or fully automated |
| **Microsoft 365 (E3/E5)**          | SharePoint, Outlook, Teams, and access to standard connectors               |

